item.title: Speaker - Azure AI Fostering Sense within XR World
item.author: thinkuldeep@gmail.com (Kuldeep Singh)
item.description: Season of AI, a virtual event series of the Microsoft Azure Developer Community by Reskill, stands as a flagship event in empowering aspiring professionals. Recently, I had the privilege of delivering a session, where I had the opportunity to guide the community and share insights from my experience in XR and AI development. It was an honor to accept this invitation, and spacial thanks to Rohit Sardana and Azkar Khan for extending the invitation.
